{"id":"lyr_5p2O5YWL5Yuk_MTk5MQ_0013","text":"被細水推翻過去 情侶一一告退","structure":{"line_index":13,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["時間","變遷","離別"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["細水","推翻","情侶","告退"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,4,9,3,3,4,4,0,5,3,3,4,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bei6","sai3","seoi2","teoi1","faan1","gwo3","heoi3","cing4","leoi5","jat1","jat1","gou3","teoi3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"被","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"細水","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"推翻","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"過去","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"情侶","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"一一","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"告退","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「細水」比喻時間的流逝，將過去的感情和關係一一推翻，情侶們也隨之離去。"},"source":{"title":"今夕是何年","artists":["李克勤"],"lyricists":["林若寧"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1991","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p2O5YWL5Yuk_MTk5MQ_0012","next_line_id":"lyr_5p2O5YWL5Yuk_MTk5MQ_0014","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
